title: Kearney Symphony Orchestra
text:
The Kearney Symphony Orchestra is the full orchestra for Kearney, Nebraska, consisting of community musicians from Central Nebraska, music instructors from the University of Nebraska-Kearney, and students from the University of Nebraska-Kearney and area high schools.  The orchestra performs four concerts each year.  The current director of the orchestra is Alison Gaines.
